{"tid":1631231,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"支共黨旗其實可以咁玩","createTime":"2019-10-06T15:02:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T06:16:11.000Z","uid":307711,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"102b227c054e66c97e9129c4da2d6068a27c7f77","tid":1631231,"uid":307711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:02:05.000Z","msg":"9.29後<br />\n反支共抗赤納粹文宣比反蒙面法spin走<br />\n其實民主 自由 反共 抗暴 自治 係五位一體，不可分割，所以我地要繼續呢方面宣傳，如果唔係會對不住全球咁多城市對我地支持<br />\n<br />\n所有手足都知燒國旗犯法，燒黨旗唔犯法，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">問題係點樣燒？</span></strong><br />\n其實最大問題係香港唔會掛黨旗，你搵唔到，自然燒唔到<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">咁點解我地唔自製？</span></strong><br />\n就算比你買到黨旗，成本都好高，買完返嚟一把火燒左佢，肉都赤埋<br />\n<br />\n其實<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jR2GAEx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjR2GAEx.png&h=82b66f4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢張支共旗只要我地簡單print出嚟，再燒左佢，已經達到文宣效果，幾乎零成本，燒自己財產亦唔犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以後每個人出嚟發夢，都帶一大疊支共旗出嚟，自然有人幫你處置佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n細膽和理非仲有一個玩法，可以直接屋企燒，當然要注意家居安全，香燭要喺化寶爐內燃燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屋企燒人地鳩知呀？<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">當然係一路燒一路拍片開心share啦！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n快d開始<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全民燒黨旗</span></strong>啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6231b5099ecce39ee921a325b00779f7ce99b368","tid":1631231,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:04:27.000Z","msg":"縱火，一個人組織非法集會，破壞社會安寧，污染"},{"pid":"f414e80aabf683f83c867dcef2ae454da415401e","tid":1631231,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:05:42.000Z","msg":"我痴左枝旗係鞋底好耐⋯⋯<br />\n無人留意到"},{"pid":"d5d4adbdf4090c6cfe9a40